dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Created and populated reference name field. 2. Fixed multipart sliver errors in Admin3 "Koussanar", "Bonconto" and "Tambacounda". 3. Fixed 64 Gap Errors. 4. Fixed nesting errors among the Admin0-3 layers.
The following was found by ITOS but not addressed in this version: 1. The slashes in Admin3 names "Sinthiou Banambe/Wouro Sidy" and "Sibassoor/Ngothie" suggest the presence of alternate names that should be separated and placed in an AltName field.
